And that comes from `uname -p`:
```sh
	UNAME_PROCESSOR=`uname -p` || UNAME_PROCESSOR=unknown
	case $UNAME_PROCESSOR in
	    unknown) UNAME_PROCESSOR=powerpc ;;
	esac
	echo ${UNAME_PROCESSOR}-apple-darwin${UNAME_RELEASE}
	exit ;;
```
